overview.shortName: EA Series Trust Strive U.S. Sem
overview.longBusinessSummary: The index is a subset of a float-adjusted capitalization weighted index of equity securities covering approximately the largest 99% of the free-float market capitalization in the U.S. stock market stock market. Under normal circumstances, at least 80% of the funds total assets (exclusive of collateral held from securities lending) will be invested in U.S. semiconductor companies. It is non-diversified.
